OL,3,CNotts County celebrate League One
OL,4,Cpromotion with city centre party
OL,6,F"This is about the supporters!" An
OL,7,Femotional tribute from Notts County
OL,8,FHead Coach Martin Paterson after
OL,9,Fguiding Notts County to promotion in
OL,10,Fhis first season in charge of the club.
OL,12,FNotts County are holding a title party
OL,13,Fin Nottingham city centre after
OL,14,Fsecuring their return to the third-
OL,15,Ftier of English football.
OL,17,FIt's the first time the club will play
OL,18,Fin League One for eleven years. Notts
OL,19,FCounty secured promotion by thrashing
OL,20,FSalford City 3-0 in the League Two
OL,21,Fplay-off on bank holiday Monday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
