OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779819070
OL,3,CNotts County celebrate League One
OL,4,Cpromotion with city centre party
OL,6,FTo champion the club's success, the
OL,7,Fplayers and staff were paraded from
OL,8,Fthe balcony of the Nottingham Council
OL,9,FHouse from 3pm today (26 May).
OL,11,FA number of players took turns to
OL,12,Fspeak to the packed crowd at Old
OL,13,FMarket Square. These included Wembley
OL,14,Fgoalscorer Ollie Norburn.
OL,16,FGoalkeeper, James Belshaw, revealed to
OL,17,FITV News Central achieving promotion
OL,18,Fwith Notts County was a dream come
OL,19,Ftrue for "a boy from Clifton," after
OL,20,Fonly joining the club in January, aged
OL,21,F35.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1779819070
OL,3,CNotts County celebrate League One
OL,4,Cpromotion with city centre party
OL,6,FBelshaw said: "A boy from Clifton,
OL,7,Fthat was a Notts fan growing up that
OL,8,Fjust had a dream to play for the club.
OL,9,FI had a dream to represent at first
OL,10,Fteam level and I got that. To then be
OL,11,Fpart of a team that did what we did at
OL,12,FWembley, to give that moment to them,
OL,13,Fthat's what he wanted to do."
OL,15,FRoad closures and diversions have been
OL,16,Fput in place around the city centre.
OL,17,FThe council's confirmed that bus and
OL,18,Ftram services will be disrupted
OL,19,Fbetween 2pm - 4:30pm with the chances
OL,20,Fof a number of short notice amendments.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
